Wrathful Avatar

Hero (level 100+) players build Wrathful Avatar charge over real time while
they are alive and active. Charge normally reaches full after 30 minutes, though
potions and other influences can quicken or slow the gathering wrath. When the
charge reaches full, use:

  avatar
  avatar end

Wrathful Avatar spends the full charge and grants 30 minutes of heightened
combat power. While active, you gain +10 strength, dexterity, and constitution,
better accuracy and criticals, harder hits, faster attacks, sharper dodges, and
a chance to absorb incoming blows in avatar fire.

The power also grants all weapon-specialization, weapon, armor, and dual-wield
permissions while it lasts. It does not stack with itself or with another
Wrathful Avatar. Use score or meter to check your current charge and charge
rate.

Use avatar end while Wrathful Avatar is active to end it immediately. This uses
the normal Avatar cleanup and leaves your avatar charge at 0%.

Divine patronage can change your charge rate. Use patron for your current
patron modifier and omens for the current world state.
